| XSS (A03) | Rendering HTML with user content | Use a templating engine with auto-escaping; set `Content-Security-Policy` via helmet |
| SSRF (A10) | Accepting URLs and fetching server-side | Allowlist hosts; block RFC1918/link-local |
| Mass assignment | `app.post('/users', (req, res) => db.create(req.body))` | Explicit whitelist of fields |
| Input validation (A03) | Any query/body/param | Validate with `zod`/`joi`, reject on failure |

Example validation pattern for when you add `/users/:id`:

```js
